title: Ebro In The Morning - BACK IN STUDIO + Guest Mayor Bill de Blasio
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 6/16.

Ebro tells us who played themselves (19:00), Laura Stylez has her patented Flashing Lights segments (12:00, 1:04:00 & 1:28:00), and NYC Mayor Bill de Blasio tries to clown Rosenberg (38:00). The Crew gives away Summer Jam Tickets, talks Nets (1:25:00) and give some Guru-like advice (1:13:00).

Please like and subscribe to Ebro In The Morning.
